│ that is not a power of 2, which violates a core assumption of the VPlan-based vectorizer   │
│ that VFs are powers of two.\n\n### 2. Analyzing `opt`'s Log\n\nThe Scalar Evolution (SE)   │
│ analysis provides crucial details about the loop's memory access patterns:\n- The          │
